data.description: Want a Winter Vacation or Retirement home in Sunny Florida?  Come to the HILLS of GATED GRAND HORIZONS, a premier 55+ community where you OWN your LAND!  This Unique Jacobson home is Customized with a Screened in covered Deck on the front to enjoy the breeze and entertain friends and neighbors.  Great curb appeal with widened driveway featuring decorative coating, landscaped lawn and tropical palm to welcome you!  Enter thru the front door to this Light, Bright OPEN floor plan with Cathedral ceilings, Transom windows over the double window in the Great room plus an air conditioned BONUS room offering Flex space for a craft/sewing room, den, home office, fitness area or mancave with views of the front landscape.  Updated features include: 2020 ROOF with 5 year warranty (4/28/25); AC is 2018 Franklin 16 SEER 3 Ton Heat Pump with 10 year warranty, thermostat and surge protector plus Double pane windows for energy efficiency. Kitchen has a convenient center island with breakfast bar, 2018 Stainless steel appliances, ceramic band to accent the counters and white cabinets.  Two spacious bedrooms at the rear of the home, Primary bedroom has a bath ensuite with Tile floors, a linen closet and full shower.  Guest bedroom has a large closet and easy access to the full guest bath with a tub/shower combination, solar tube and tile floors. Well Maintained home on a quiet cul-de-sac street with no rear neighbors has been newly painted inside so you can MOVE RIGHT IN! Located in east Pasco County, just North of Tampa in Zephyrhills, within one mile of shopping, restaurants, bowling, theaters, library, medical facilities, hospital and YMCA.  No CDD fees and Low HOA in this Community with Resident owned amenities: Heated Pool, Hot tub, Clubhouse with billiards, commercial kitchen, craft room, library/game room, shuffleboard, bocce, onsite entertainment, planned activities and travel excursions... CALL TODAY and see why this IS the place to BE!
